article_title: Video: ‘What Does the Fox Say?’ Takes Off in Singapore
article_text:
In this week’s Digits show, the WSJ’s Yun-Hee Kim shows us three smartphones that don’t sport an Apple or Samsung logo, Diana Jou explores a Chinese air-filtration mask that delivers pollution alerts and Ramy Inocencio asks, “What does the fox say?” in Trending in Asia.

Follow WSJ Asia on Twitter @WSJAsia.
